sed for radio and TV transmissions.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2878, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.5520815331441963, \"rank\": 0.4634007417606316, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some Parisians\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"the 324-metre (1,063-foot) tower\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"latticed steel girders\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"a temporary attraction\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2865}, {\"ngram\": \"a working telecoms tower\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"radio and TV transmissions\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Iron Lady\\\" has since become the capital's symbol and is one of the world's top tourist attractions, with 6.3 million visitors in 2023.\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The \\\"Iron Lady\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital's symbol\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's top tourist attractions\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"6.3 million visitors\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3133}]}]}"